---
title: Nan's Veggie Mince Spaghetti Bolognese with Garden Salad & Flaked Almonds
description: Golden ropes of spaghetti coated in a rich, creamy tomato sauce and veggie mince. Finished with a scattering of almonds
and a complementary salad, this is nothing short of a small bite of heaven.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64a287fb91cac2bc8b808782-3a1952a9.jpeg
